metadata.title: Wrangell Mountain Aerial Photographs

creators.name: Ducks Unlimited Inc., Pacific Meridian Resources

metadata.description: Data Type: Remotely Sensed Data;   Small number of high altitude photos of the Wrangell Mountains. There are 29 positive transparencies from 1974 (these are very dark) and 23 transparencies from 1984.
